HEADWORD: Strapple
<hw>Strap"ple</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To hold or bind
with, or as with, a strap; to entangle.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Chapman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
